WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
Mindful stress reset in one minute.

00:03.200 --> 00:07.000
Inhale through the nose for four counts.

00:07.200 --> 00:11.000
Hold gently for four counts—shoulders relaxed.

00:11.200 --> 00:16.000
Exhale slowly for six counts through pursed lips.

00:16.200 --> 00:20.000
Repeat the 4‑4‑6 cycle four times.

00:20.200 --> 00:24.000
On each exhale, soften your jaw and drop your shoulders.

00:24.200 --> 00:28.000
Return to the task with a calmer baseline.

00:28.200 --> 00:32.000
Use this micro‑reset between focus sprints.
